ourStory.title: our story
ourStory.paragraph:
A home is the warmth of a loving family united...
A home is a spring of memories, a place to escape reality...
A home is family gathered around the dinner table filled with traditional home Cooked meals...
A home is a gathering of friends, on echoing laugh and an everlasting feel of kindness and safety.
This is enab,
ourStory.seconedPara: Enab in English means Grapes. The idea behind the concept is that Enab Beirut will serve as a destination at which families, friends (old 8. new), co-workers, etc. can rneet for a traditionally prepared Lebanese meal, bringing them together to share, create and add to their rnemories thus furThering their bond each as a member of the 'Grape Vine.'

branch1.head: What are grapes?
branch1.paragraph: Enab In English Means Grapes. The Idea Behind The Concept Is That Enab Beirut Will Serve As A Destination At Which Families, Friends (Old 8. New), Co-Workers, Etc. Can Rneet For A Traditionally Prepared Lebanese Meal, Bringing Them Together To Share, Create And Add To Their Rnemories Thus FurThering Their Bond Each As A Member Of The 'Grape Vine.'

branch2.head: When was Enab Beirut established and why is enab?
branch2.paragraph: Established in 2012, Enab Beirut is the go to place for people seeking the taste of a traditional home cooked labanese meal. The concept was built on the need to provide customers with. experience that not only included the taste they sought, but also the ambiance that was missing at other lebanese restaurants within the market.

branch3.head: What about our branches in the Middle East and North Africa?
branch3.paragraph: In keeping with the traditionslam of our concept our Interior decor has been chosen to further add to the experience of being at home although not all locations can be identical, we guarantee that our customers will have  the some experience whether at our Flagship Outlet in Beirut, or in any one of our Franchisee's Outlets within the Middle East and North Africa Region. We maintain our standards  through a highly-trained team that are dedicated to ensuring our standards are as they were when we established our Flagship Outlet in 2012.

branch4.head: Our success at the local and regional levels
branch4.paragraph: After succeeding in the locally, the next step was to expand regionally. Enab has established a name for itself through constantly providing its clientele with impeccable food and outstanding service. This reputation has drawn interest from around the region and we now successfully have 5 Franchised Outlets both locally and regionally, with more still to come,
